WEBVTT

05:14.750 --> 05:16.210 line:80%
to order wedding clothes.

05:16.400 --> 05:18.310 line:80%
Upon hearing that the army
is recruiting in Chongzhou,

05:18.310 --> 05:20.230 line:80%
everyone is rushing

05:20.670 --> 05:22.520 line:80%
to get married to secure an heir.

05:23.040 --> 05:24.230 line:80%
My staff in the shop

05:24.230 --> 05:25.290 line:80%
can barely keep up.
